<p></p>
<p><tags><tag kind="heading3">### </tag></tags>Smart Lists</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags>If enabled, hitting <element kind="code" startTag="`">↩︎</element> will automatically add another list item, while <element kind="code" startTag="`">⌥↩︎</element> will just create a new paragraph</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags>Enable Smart Lists via “Edit › Substitutions”</p>
<p></p>
<p><tags><tag kind="heading3">### </tag></tags>Media</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags>Drag’n’drop images and PDFs into the editor to create a text object which holds the item</p>
<p></p>
<p><tags><tag kind="heading3">### </tag></tags>Text Objects</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘</element>-Click to select</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags>Double-click to open text object popover</p>
<p></p>
<p><tags><tag kind="heading3">### </tag></tags>Text Object Popovers</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⌘↩︎</element> to close and move insertion point forward</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">esc</element> to close and keep object selected</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags><element kind="code" startTag="`">⇥</element> to switch between input fields</p>
<p><tags><tag kind="unorderedList">- </tag></tags>Drag popover to tear it off and place it anywhere on screen</p>
